Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.23,0:23:13.49,cned,NTP,0,0,0,,有人在呼喚我
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.79,0:23:18.96,cned,NTP,0,0,0,,在某處呼喚我
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.53,0:23:24.77,cned,NTP,0,0,0,,溫柔的聲音
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.09,0:23:27.75,cned,NTP,0,0,0,,從遠方傳來
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.49,0:23:30.95,cned,NTP,0,0,0,,心為之而動
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.23,0:23:34.38,cned,NTP,0,0,0,,請告訴我
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.79,0:23:42.37,cned,NTP,0,0,0,,這悲傷的預感將是否成真
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.49,0:23:47.53,cned,NTP,0,0,0,,未曾知曉的心願
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.10,0:23:54.88,cned,NTP,0,0,0,,漸漸浮現
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.47,0:24:00.71,cned,NTP,0,0,0,,一直有個夢
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.78,0:24:06.81,cned,NTP,0,0,0,,夢中迷惘 而充滿自由
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.65,0:24:12.72,cned,NTP,0,0,0,,輕聲許下願望
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.21,0:24:18.84,cned,NTP,0,0,0,,好想和大家一起
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.41,0:24:24.57,cned,NTP,0,0,0,,相視而笑
